 223         protected override void OnPaint(PaintEventArgs& args)
 224         {
 225             try
 226             {
 227                 if (Debug.Paint())
 228                 {
 229                     Rect r(Location(), GetSize());
 230                     LogView* log = Application.GetLogView();
 231                     if (log != null)
 232                     {
 233                         log->WriteLine("MenuBar.OnPaint: " + r.ToString());
 234                     }
 235                 }
 236                 if (!MenuBoxAdded())
 237                 {
 238                     SetMenuBoxAdded();
 239                     AddMenuBox();
 240                 }
 241                 args.graphics.Clear(BackgroundColor());
 242                 if (MenuChanged())
 243                 {
 244                     ResetMenuChanged();
 245                     CollectShortcuts();
 246                     Size size = GetSize();
 247                     size.h = cast<int>(GetFont().GetHeight(args.graphics));
 248                     size.h = size.h + DefaultPadding().Vertical();
 249                     SetSize(size);
 250                     LocateMenuItems(args.graphics, size);
 251                 }
 252                 DrawMenuItems(args, false, Location());
 253                 base->OnPaint(args);
 254             }
 255             catch (const Exception& ex)
 256             {
 257                 MessageBox.Show(ex.Message());
 258             }
 259         }
 260         private void LocateMenuItems(Graphics& graphics, const Size& size)
 261         {
 262             Rect itemRect(Location(), Size(0, size.h));
 263             Padding padding = DefaultPadding();
 264             PointF origin(0, 0);
 265             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 266             while (child != null)
 267             {
 268                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 269                 {
 270                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 271                     Padding menuItemPadding = menuItem->DefaultPadding();
 272                     RectF r = graphics.MeasureStringChecked(menuItem->Text(), GetFont(), origin, Format());
 273                     int w = cast<int>(r.size.w) + padding.Horizontal() + menuItemPadding.Horizontal();
 274                     itemRect.size.w = w;
 275                     menuItem->SetLocation(itemRect.location);
 276                     menuItem->SetSize(itemRect.size);
 277                     menuItem->CalculateChildRect(graphics, GetFont(), Format(), Point(itemRect.location.x, itemRect.location.y + itemRect.size.h));
 278                     itemRect.location.x = itemRect.location.x + w;
 279                 }
 280                 child = child->NextSibling();
 281             }
 282         }

 295         }

 329             {

 331                 if (it != shortcuts.CEnd())

 333                     MenuItem* menuItem = it->second;
 334                     if (menuItem->IsEnabled())
 335                     {
 336                         menuItem->DoClick();

 338                     }
 339                 }
 340             }

 354         protected override void OnMouseMove(MouseEventArgs& args)
 355         {
 356             ResetMenuInvalidated();
 357             base->OnMouseMove(args);
 358             bool handled = false;
 359             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 360             while (child != null)
 361             {
 362                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 363                 {
 364                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 365                     if (!menuItem->Contains(args.location))
 366                     {
 367                         menuItem->ResetSelected(this);
 368                         if (menuItem->MouseInClient())
 369                         {
 370                             menuItem->ResetMouseInClient();
 371                             menuItem->DoMouseLeave(this);
 372                         }
 373                     }
 374                 }
 375                 child = child->NextSibling();
 376             }
 377             child = children.FirstChild();
 378             while (child != null)
 379             {
 380                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 381                 {
 382                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 383                     if (menuItem->Contains(args.location))
 384                     {
 385                         menuItem->SetSelected(this);
 386                         if (!menuItem->MouseInClient())
 387                         {
 388                             menuItem->SetMouseInClient();
 389                             menuItem->DoMouseEnter(IsOpen(), this);
 390                         }
 391                         else
 392                         {
 393                             menuItem->DoMouseMove(args);
 394                         }
 395                         handled = true;
 396                     }
 397                 }
 398                 child = child->NextSibling();
 399             }
 400             if (!handled)
 401             {
 402                 if (IsOpen())
 403                 {
 404                     if (latestOpenedMenuItem != null)
 405                     {
 406                         Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 407                         while (child != null && !handled)
 408                         {
 409                             if (child is MenuItem*)
 410                             {
 411                                 MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 412                                 if (menuItem->IsSameOrParentOf(latestOpenedMenuItem))
 413                                 {
 414                                     menuItem->DispatchMouseMove(args, handled, this);
 415                                 }
 416                             }
 417                             child = child->NextSibling();
 418                         }
 419                     }
 420                 }
 421             }
 422             if (MenuInvalidated())
 423             {
 424                 InvalidateMenu();
 425             }
 426         }

 430         }
 431         protected override void OnMouseLeave()
 432         {
 433             ResetMenuInvalidated();
 434             base->OnMouseLeave();
 435             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 436             while (child != null)
 437             {
 438                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 439                 {
 440                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 441                     if (menuItem->MouseInClient() || menuItem->Children().IsEmpty())
 442                     {
 443                         menuItem->ResetSelected(this);
 444                         menuItem->ResetMouseInClient();
 445                         Point mousePos;
 446                         WinGetMessagePos(mousePos.x, mousePos.y);
 447                         mousePos = ScreenToClient(mousePos);
 448                         if (menuItem != latestOpenedMenuItem || !menuItem->UnionRectContains(mousePos))
 449                         {
 450                             menuItem->DoMouseLeave(this);
 451                         }
 452                     }
 453                     else
 454                     {
 455                         menuItem->ResetSelected(this);
 456                         menuItem->ResetMouseInClient();
 457                     }
 458                 }
 459                 child = child->NextSibling();
 460             }
 461             if (MenuInvalidated())
 462             {
 463                 InvalidateMenu();
 464             }
 465         }
 466         internal override void InvalidateMenu()
 467         {
 468             Invalidate();
 469             Rect menuRect;
 470             Component* child = children.FirstChild();
 471             while (child != null)
 472             {
 473                 if (child is MenuItem*)
 474                 {
 475                     MenuItem* menuItem = cast<MenuItem*>(child);
 476                     if (menuItem->GetState() == MenuItem.State.open)
 477                     {
 478                         menuItem->GetOpenRect(menuRect);
 479                     }
 480                 }
 481                 child = child->NextSibling();
 482             }
 483             if (IsOpen())
 484             {
 485                 if (menuBox != null)
 486                 {
 487                     menuBox->SetPaintThisMenuBox(true);
 488                     menuBox->SetLocation(Point(Location().x + menuRect.location.x, Location().y + menuRect.location.y));
 489                     menuBox->SetSize(menuRect.size);
 490                     Control* parentControl = ParentControl();
 491                     Control* topControl = null;
 492                     if (parentControl != null)
 493                     {
 494                         topControl = parentControl->TopControl();
 495                     }
 496                     menuBox->BringToFront();
 497                     menuBox->Show();
 498                     menuBox->Invalidate();
 499                     menuBox->Update();
 500                     if (topControl != null)
 501                     {
 502                         topControl->BringToFront();
 503                     }
 504                 }
 505             }
 506             else
 507             {
 508                 if (menuBox != null)
 509                 {
 510                     menuBox->SetPaintThisMenuBox(false);
 511                     menuBox->Hide();
 512                 }
 513                 InvalidateParentRect(menuRect);
 514                 Control* parentControl = ParentControl();
 515                 if (parentControl != null)
 516                 {
 517                     parentControl->Update();
 518                 }
 519             }
 520         }

 531                 }

 533             }

 535         internal bool HandleAccessKey(wchar accessKey, Keys keyCode, bool& wantsKeys)
 536         {
 537             ResetMenuInvalidated();
 538             LogView* logView = Application.GetLogView();
 539             if (logView != null)
 540             {
 541                 string s = "MENUBAR: access key = '" + ToString(accessKey) + "' " + ToHexString(cast<ushort>(accessKey)) + ", key code = " + string(keyCodeStr[cast<int>(keyCode)]);
 542                 logView->WriteLine(s);
 543             }
 544             if (accessKey == '\0' && keyCode == Keys.none)
 545             {
 546                 if (selectedMenuItem == null)
 547                 {
 548                     MenuItem* firstMenuItem = GetFirstMenuItem();
 549                     if (firstMenuItem != null)
 550                     {
 551                         SetOpen();
 552                         SetSelectedMenuItem(firstMenuItem);
 553                         wantsKeys = true;
 554                         InvalidateMenu();
 555                         return true;
 556                     }
 557                 }
 558                 else
 559                 {
 560                     SetClosed();
 561                     MenuItem* openedMenuItem = GetOpenedMenuItem();
 562                     if (openedMenuItem != null)
 563                     {
 564                         openedMenuItem->SetState(MenuItem.State.closed, this);
 565                     }
 566                     selectedMenuItem->ResetSelected(this);
 567                     SetSelectedMenuItem(null);
 568                     wantsKeys = false;
 569                     InvalidateMenu();
 570                     return true;
 571                 }
 572             }
 573             else if (accessKey != '\0' && keyCode == Keys.none)
 574             {
 575                 MenuItem* menuItem = GetMenuItemByAccessKey(accessKey);
 576                 if (menuItem != null)
 577                 {
 578                     MenuItem* firstMenuItem = menuItem->GetFirstMenuItem();
 579                     if (firstMenuItem != null)
 580                     {
 581                         if (selectedMenuItem != null)
 582                         {
 583                             MenuItem* openedMenuItem = GetOpenedMenuItem();
 584                             if (openedMenuItem != null)
 585                             {
 586                                 openedMenuItem->SetState(MenuItem.State.closed, this);
 587                             }
 588                         }
 589                         SetOpen();
 590                         menuItem->SetState(MenuItem.State.open, this);
 591                         SetSelectedMenuItem(firstMenuItem);
 592                         wantsKeys = true;
 593                         InvalidateMenu();
 594                         return true;
 595                     }
 596                 }
 597             }
 598             else if (accessKey == '\0' && keyCode != Keys.none)
 599             {
 600                 if (keyCode == Keys.menu)
 601                 {
 602                     wantsKeys = true;
 603                     return true;
 604                 }
 605                 else
 606                 {
 607                     if (selectedMenuItem != null)
 608                     {
 609                         MenuItem* parentItem = selectedMenuItem->GetParentMenuItem();
 610                         bool handled = selectedMenuItem->HandleKey(keyCode, wantsKeys, parentItem, this);
 611                         return handled;
 612                     }
 613                 }
 614             }
 615             if (MenuInvalidated())
 616             {
 617                 InvalidateMenu();
 618             }
 619             wantsKeys = false;
 620             return false;
 621         }

 623         {
 624             OnMouseDown(args);
 625         }

 633             {

 641                         return;
 642                     }
 643                 }

 645             }

 648                 SetClosed();
 649                 SetLatestOpenedMenuItem(null);

 651                 while (child != null)
